                <head>8. Summary of Conclusions of a Policy Review Committee Meeting<note n="1"
                        type="source" xml:id="d8fn1">Source: Carter Library, National Security
                        Council, Institutional Files, 1977–1981, Box 60, <gloss target="#t_PRC_1"
                            >PRC</gloss> 770006—Cuba [2]. Secret. Drafted by <persName
                            corresp="#p_PRA_1">Pastor</persName>. The meeting was held in the White
                        House Situation Room. Minutes of this meeting are in the Carter Library,
                        National Security Affairs, Brzezinski Material, Brzezinski Office File,
                        Country Chron File, Box 7, Cuba, 2–5/77.</note>
                </head>
